snippet.title: Jaws.io Official Game Trailer
snippet.description: DUN dun, DUN dun…. JAWS is now causing chaos on mobile in this fun and fast-paced multiplayer hyper-casual io game. Submerge yourself in the waters of Amity Island and rack up the points by avoiding being eaten, saving swimmers and finishing the round with the top score as JAWS!
